ETrun client files
==================

Compatibility
-------------

Supported OS:

* Windows 7 and newer (32-bit & 64-bit)
* Linux (32-bit & 64-bit)
* macOS (Intel 64-bit and Apple Silicon arm64)

Check https://github.com/ETrun/ETrun/blob/master/README.md for more information.

Installing
----------

Put ETrun-XXX.pk3 in etrun/ folder.

Refer to https://etrun.readthedocs.io/en/latest/client_cvars/ to configure your settings.
